        <item>
            <title>Call Recorder 0.5.2</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 04 Jun 2026 15:41:17 +0100</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Call Recorder 0.5.2</h2>
                <p>Bug fixes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Voice recognition (speaker naming) now works reliably - fixes a sample-rate bug that corrupted enrolled voiceprints. If you enrolled a voice on an earlier version, please delete it and re-enrol (Preferences &gt; Voices).</li>
                    <li>Pre-call echo removed: the brief echo at the very start of a recording (the calling app's self-monitor/sidetone before the call connects) is now suppressed. In-call audio is unchanged.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
