        <item>
            <title>Call Recorder 0.5.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 04 Jun 2026 11:17:00 +0100</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Call Recorder 0.5.0</h2>
                <p>Major feature release:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Wideband audio: recordings now capture at 32kHz HE-AAC for noticeably crisper, clearer voices (especially the remote party), at about the same file size</li>
                    <li>New floating in-call pill with pause, stop &amp; save, and cancel controls, plus a live audio spectrum</li>
                    <li>Gapless pause/resume (also from the menu)</li>
                    <li>Voice-print enrolment: enrol people's voices in Preferences &gt; Voices so transcripts name speakers instead of "Speaker 1/2"</li>
                    <li>Auto-discards a recording when a call is answered on your iPhone instead of the Mac</li>
                    <li>Interface refresh and Preferences fixes (sidebar, version display)</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <sparkle:version>22</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
